1.1 Execution context in Javascript
-> Everything in javascript happens inside an execution context.
->Imagine execution context is big box where whole js code is get executed.

1.2  Variable Environement of Execution context
->Execution context is like a big box. it has two components in it.
a. Memory component
->this the where all variables and functions are stored as key-value pairs.
->this memory component is also know as Varaible environment.

eg-1:
Memory Component    |     Code Component

key :value                 // code //
a:10
function:{
    -----
}

b. Code component
->this the place where whole javascipt code is executed.
->this the place code is executed one line at a time.
->it is also known as thread of execution.


1.3 Javascript is synchronous single-threaded language
